1
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:52,959
Uncle Kun

2
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:03,799
Thank you, Mr. Liang, for deciding to adopt Xiao Qi.

3
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,680
He has always been our...

4
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,159
most well-behaved and obedient child here.

5
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,360
Blood! Blood!

6
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,840
There's blood everywhere!

7
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:10,800
Blood!

8
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,319
There's blood everywhere!

9
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:14,199
What's wrong? There's blood everywhere!

10
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,080
Blood!

11
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:16,120
What's happening? Blood!

12
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,280
There's blood everywhere!

13
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,080
What's wrong? What's wrong?

14
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,520
It's everywhere!

15
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:20,520
What's going on? Everywhere...

16
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,800
There's blood everywhere!

17
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:24,919
Don't hurt Xiao Qi! He's having an episode!

18
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,680
He's the one.

19
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:52,000
You can now...

20
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,719
put away the mask.

21
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,520
I heard from the director...

22
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,520
that the child...

23
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,039
loses control when he sees blood.

24
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:05,680
Flies into a rage.

25
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,159
If you want to wear a mask,

26
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,719
you have to...

27
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,840
weld it to your face.

28
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:24,159
Don't use paint anymore.

29
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,919
If we're doing this,

30
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,400
we do it for real.

31
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,719
Real blood...

32
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,759
will turn brown

33
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,400
within three minutes.

34
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,479
Okay.

35
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:53,280
I'll send you to the most suitable place.

36
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:54,960
Drink this.

37
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,240
All right.

38
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,800
The police station you're going to...

39
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,720
has a man named Guan Renjie.

40
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,680
He keeps planting moles in our organization.

41
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,160
Help me root him out.

42
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,439
Don't move!

43
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:10,759
What are you doing?

44
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:11,360
Don't move!

45
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,839
Let go of me!

46
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,759
Help!

47
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,920
Help!

48
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:18,639
Help!

49
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:26,759
Are you okay?

50
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,160
You're from the East District.

51
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,839
Why are you on duty in the West District?

52
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,399
Reporting, Superintendent Guan.

53
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,279
I'm not on duty.

54
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,879
I'm here investigating the 2002 Cangfeng smuggling case.

55
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:41,839
Looking for leads.

56
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,800
You're interested in that case?

57
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,360
I asked you here today...

58
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,000
for a personal matter.

59
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,920
To thank you for saving my daughter.

60
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,879
Let's have dinner this weekend.

61
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,040
Thank you, sir.

62
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,160
Sir,

63
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:11,920
you're too kind.

64
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,680
Keep me in mind for good things like this.

65
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,600
I'm quick on my feet,

66
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,480
tight-lipped,

67
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,959
and reliable.

68
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,800
Haven't eaten yet, have you?

69
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:27,959
This is for you.

70
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:35,759
Sir,

71
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,040
you're a real lifesaver.

72
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:40,839
Take your time eating.

73
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,240
Although in the Cangfeng smuggling case,

74
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,720
our undercover agent was unfortunately exposed,

75
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,879
thanks to your efforts,

76
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,600
we still seized the contraband.

77
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:21,360
Superintendent Guan also highly recommended you.

78
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,439
I am grateful for Superintendent Guan's appreciation.

79
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,920
Fortunately, my performance review scores...

80
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:27,720
are all ranked first.

81
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:30,839
So I haven't let down the leadership's favor.

82
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,920
I heard that you and Superintendent Guan's adopted daughter...

83
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,680
are quite close.

84
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:38,240
Although she was adopted by Superintendent Guan,

85
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,240
her biological family background is very complex.

86
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,680
Her parents attempted to bribe a councilor,

87
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:46,160
and her brother got addicted to gambling...

88
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,959
and committed suicide over loan shark debts.

89
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:51,399
You should reconsider your relationship with her,

90
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,439
so it doesn't affect your promotion.

91
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:56,800
I'm sorry, sir.

92
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:58,959
I apologize for the rumors you've heard.

93
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,279
It's only because of Superintendent Guan...

94
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:03,120
that I've had some interactions with Miss Hao.

95
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,199
But at most,

96
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:05,560
we are just ordinary friends.

97
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,560
Let's break up.

98
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,360
Why?

99
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,160
We...

100
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,319
have always been...

101
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,360
a secret romance.

102
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,240
No.

103
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,519
It doesn't even count as a secret romance.

104
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,399
At best,

105
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,240
it's just a casual fling.

106
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:40,159
You have a better job now.

107
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,919
You should put yourself first.

108
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,960
I'm being transferred.

109
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,279
It's not like I'm not coming back.

110
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:52,360
Why do we have to break up?

111
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:55,799
It's my fault.

112
00:08:58,679 --> 00:09:00,000
I'm not good enough for you.

113
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,120
I've fallen in love with someone else.

114
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,840
Who is he?

115
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,720
You haven't wanted to see me lately.

116
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:24,320
I asked Superintendent Guan, but he was evasive.

117
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,240
What exactly happened?

118
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,399
You... tell me.

119
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,360
Zhou Ziheng.

120
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,120
Let's not contact each other anymore.

121
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:43,879
I wish you all the best.

122
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,360
Hao Yu.

123
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,320
I was planning to dump her anyway.

124
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,360
Now it works out perfectly.

125
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,480
Ziheng.

126
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:08,799
Uncle Kun.

127
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:11,120
I've been transferred back to Selong Port now.

128
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,519
Good.

129
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:19,679
With you back, things will be much easier for me.

130
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,399
While you were away these past few years,

131
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:23,840
there have been flies buzzing around us.

132
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,320
That Guan Renjie.

133
00:10:27,799 --> 00:10:29,360
Find a way to get rid of him.

134
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:30,639
Also,

135
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:34,279
that list of informants in his hands,

136
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:36,360
find a way to get your hands on that too.

137
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:40,320
Yes.

138
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,399
Guan Renjie went up to the Wugang Street rooftop.

139
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:50,080
Weihao can make his move now.

140
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:58,159
You three, go down.

141
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,000
The rest of you, chase him!

142
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,360
Colleagues at the station said

143
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:06,440
Liang Zhaokun sent Cangfeng men

144
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,360
and tracked us here.

145
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:10,399
You go first.

146
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:11,279
Okay.

147
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:22,960
Go investigate Hao Yu.

148
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,720
Zhijie's sweetheart.

149
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,360
The person chosen to replace Guan Renjie at the station...

150
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:33,440
once it's decided,

151
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,480
tell me immediately.

152
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:42,960
It's me.

153
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:52,480
Don't move!

154
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:02,960
Cuff him.

155
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:19,879
Uncle Kun.

156
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,759
Look at this, look at this.

157
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,480
That Jiali really is something.

158
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:26,519
She has no sense of limits.

159
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,919
Made you suffer.

160
00:12:30,039 --> 00:12:31,840
I have to thank her for striking first.

161
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:34,879
Now that I've transferred back,

162
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:36,360
I can't just do nothing.

163
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,279
I didn't want to arrest Weihao,

164
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:39,519
or investigate Cangfeng.

165
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,240
She attacked and injured me.

166
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,120
It was just a minor injury.

167
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:44,960
That's good.

168
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,919
I broke this leg myself.

169
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,600
This way, I don't have to go on duty.

170
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,039
I can legitimately

171
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:54,360
avoid watching Cangfeng so closely.

172
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,559
Good.

173
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:13,039
Tomorrow, Ah Jie is delivering a batch of toys to an old friend.

174
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:16,000
If you hear wind of it at the station,

175
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:17,960
you know what to do, right?

176
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:18,960
Naturally.

177
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:22,440
Rest assured.

178
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,440
That's good.

179
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,559
If you do well,

180
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,000
just like before,

181
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,279
you'll keep rising in the ranks.

182
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,480
If something goes wrong,

183
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:45,399
those tapes of our past conversations...

184
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:50,039
I often take them out and listen to them.

185
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,360
And those injuries on your neck...

186
00:13:57,879 --> 00:13:59,519
your superiors at the station

187
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:03,519
still think you were injured in the line of duty, right?

188
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,360
Trying to threaten me?

189
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:32,679
Trying to treat me like a dog forever?

190
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,639
Using me, abusing me.

191
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:37,360
Now is the perfect time to get rid of you.

192
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:38,759
I deliberately hid the fact

193
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,399
that Hao Yu is investigating Cangfeng.

194
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,759
I even helped Hao Yu get off the hook,

195
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:45,080
just so I could use Hao Yu

196
00:14:45,919 --> 00:14:46,759
to get rid of you.

197
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,600
Hao Yu.

198
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,519
Why is she here?

199
00:14:56,279 --> 00:14:57,120
How could it be such a coincidence?

200
00:14:58,519 --> 00:15:01,080
The person who's been passing Cangfeng intel to Superintendent Guan...

201
00:15:01,759 --> 00:15:02,399
It's her.

202
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,039
PC9527, copy that.

203
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:07,519
Coordinates: Wugang Street.

204
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:09,840
There are very few cameras in this area.

205
00:15:10,279 --> 00:15:11,720
Did you notice the license plates of the surrounding cars?

206
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:16,559
I just saw a car driving out,

207
00:15:16,879 --> 00:15:18,320
but I didn't get a clear look at the license plate.

208
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,519
No other suspicious vehicles

209
00:15:20,559 --> 00:15:21,200
or personnel have been spotted so far.

210
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,639
Go investigate Hao Yu.

211
00:15:24,799 --> 00:15:26,360
Zhijie's sweetheart.

212
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,519
It really is Hao Yu.

213
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:06,799
Guan Renjie's phone...

214
00:16:06,919 --> 00:16:08,360
No matter how hard we try, we can't crack it.

215
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,440
But Hao Yu and I used to

216
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,360
play poetry guessing games.

217
00:16:13,399 --> 00:16:14,279
We can give it a try.

218
00:16:14,679 --> 00:16:16,279
Can we trick Hao Yu into coming out first,

219
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,840
see what the situation is,

220
00:16:18,559 --> 00:16:19,919
and gather more information?

221
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,679
Ten years, living and dead are lost to each other.

222
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:29,559
Though I try not to think of it,

223
00:16:30,679 --> 00:16:31,360
I can never forget.

224
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:43,799
I knew it was you.

225
00:16:44,399 --> 00:16:45,600
I should have guessed it was you.

226
00:16:46,159 --> 00:16:47,559
I should have known it was you too.

227
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,879
After all, Godfather valued you the most.

228
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:51,480
It's my fault.

229
00:16:51,799 --> 00:16:52,600
It's all my fault.

230
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:53,960
Tell me,

231
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:57,519
who is the dirty cop colluding with Liang Zhaokun?

232
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:04,880
I'm sorry.

233
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,680
We are also investigating.

234
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:10,720
I was so scared.

235
00:17:12,039 --> 00:17:12,640
You've suffered so much.

236
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,160
I was so scared.

237
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:17,480
Since she seems to still have feelings for me,

238
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:18,839
and I so easily

239
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:20,720
regained her trust,

240
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:23,759
then I should make good use of her.

241
00:17:28,519 --> 00:17:29,839
Ji Zhijie.

242
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,480
It's Ji Zhijie again.

243
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,480
Why does he get to be Liang Zhaokun's wolf,

244
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,720
and still have Hao Yu?

245
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:38,279
Why am I just Liang Zhaokun's dog?

246
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:39,759
Why?

247
00:17:40,119 --> 00:17:42,319
And he's with my former lover.

248
00:17:43,359 --> 00:17:45,119
Hao Yu is my best chance

249
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,440
to get rid of Liang Zhaokun.

250
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,200
You've been investigating for half a year,

251
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:52,559
and you haven't found a single thing on that girl.

252
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,720
I'm sorry, Uncle Kun.

253
00:17:57,039 --> 00:17:57,880
I'll do it as soon as possible.

254
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,480
I might have to trouble you this time.

255
00:18:11,119 --> 00:18:13,039
Find out the time and place of the deal ASAP.

256
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:15,240
As long as we work together well,

257
00:18:16,599 --> 00:18:18,519
we will definitely catch them all this time.

258
00:18:21,359 --> 00:18:21,960
When that time comes,

259
00:18:22,839 --> 00:18:24,279
you can completely break free from them.

260
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:28,759
And we

261
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:32,839
can

262
00:18:33,599 --> 00:18:34,240
start over.

263
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,200
I know all of this already.

264
00:18:41,599 --> 00:18:43,279
I'm afraid there will be more people around soon.

265
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,160
I'm leaving first.

266
00:18:50,799 --> 00:18:52,440
Once I destroy Cangfeng,

267
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,839
destroy you, Liang Zhaokun,

268
00:18:55,359 --> 00:18:56,640
and then destroy Ji Zhijie,

269
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:58,559
I'll earn the merit,

270
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:00,920
and win back Hao Yu.

271
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:05,160
I will be the one who truly comes clean.

272
00:19:07,799 --> 00:19:09,160
None of you,

273
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:09,960
absolutely no one,

274
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:13,000
can threaten or use me anymore.

275
00:19:13,599 --> 00:19:15,000
From now on,

276
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:17,400
you can only be used

277
00:19:18,079 --> 00:19:19,200
and controlled by me.

278
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:36,759
Regarding this case,

279
00:19:37,119 --> 00:19:37,519
we...

280
00:19:37,519 --> 00:19:38,160
Superintendent Lin,

281
00:19:41,799 --> 00:19:43,799
Cangfeng's Ji Zhijie will trade with Sucha.

282
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:45,400
My informant has already found out

283
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,720
the specific time and location of the deal.

284
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:48,200
I request maximum backup.

285
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,720
Is your informant reliable?

286
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,039
I guarantee it with my badge.

287
00:20:00,359 --> 00:20:01,240
Pass me the pliers.

288
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:07,160
Here.

289
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,440
If I can't fix it,

290
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,640
we'll wait for Feilong and Feihu to get back

291
00:20:18,799 --> 00:20:19,720
and let them handle it.

292
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:21,960
Feilong, Feihu, Feiying...

293
00:20:22,319 --> 00:20:23,519
I raised them all

294
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,559
since they were in diapers.

295
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:27,720
I know everything they know.

296
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,519
I'm much better than them.

297
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,079
What's this typhoon called again?

298
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:49,559
It's pretty intense.

299
00:21:25,839 --> 00:21:26,880
I didn't expect that before leaving,

300
00:21:27,599 --> 00:21:29,599
I'd experience a moment like this in Selong Port.

301
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,960
I heard when I was born,

302
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,359
I was thrown into a locker.

303
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,279
I don't know who my parents are.

304
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,000
I don't know who I am either.

305
00:21:45,359 --> 00:21:46,880
Someone finally picked me up,

306
00:21:47,079 --> 00:21:48,799
only to sell me off all over the place.

307
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:51,400
To survive,

308
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:53,920
I ran and fled, fled and ran.

309
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,599
I still remember back then,

310
00:21:58,599 --> 00:22:01,000
when I was scavenging for food in the trash,

311
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:03,319
people would rob me.

312
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,440
That was when I met Uncle Kun.

313
00:22:11,119 --> 00:22:12,079
Uncle Kun adopted me.

314
00:22:25,519 --> 00:22:27,279
Back then, Uncle Kun said he chose me

315
00:22:29,039 --> 00:22:30,200
because everyone else ran away,

316
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,799
and even though I was the smallest,

317
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:32,920
I dared to stand up to him.

318
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:36,759
He also said

319
00:22:39,759 --> 00:22:41,920
I was different from the other kids he adopted.

320
00:22:44,559 --> 00:22:45,480
He said they were like dogs,

321
00:22:46,359 --> 00:22:47,039
but I was like a wolf.

322
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:52,519
But if it weren't for survival,

323
00:22:52,519 --> 00:22:53,640
who would want to be a wolf?

324
00:22:54,079 --> 00:22:55,680
To keep living a good life,

325
00:22:57,599 --> 00:22:58,759
and to repay Uncle Kun,

326
00:23:01,519 --> 00:23:02,400
I had to become that...

327
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:04,839
that fiercest wolf charging at the front.

328
00:24:04,319 --> 00:24:05,200
Sometimes,

329
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:06,480
I really did forget

330
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:08,319
what it's like to live like a human...

331
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:11,160
what that feels like.

332
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,119
But when I met you,

333
00:24:17,119 --> 00:24:17,759
you told me...

334
00:24:23,119 --> 00:24:24,000
you told me...

335
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,359
told me...

336
00:24:31,599 --> 00:24:33,480
you didn't care if I was man or monster.

337
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:56,960
Hao Yu.

338
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,400
When we get to the UK,

339
00:25:02,519 --> 00:25:04,000
and have our own house,

340
00:25:05,759 --> 00:25:07,039
have our own yard...

341
00:25:15,119 --> 00:25:15,960
At that time,

342
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:18,519
you'll read books,

343
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:20,119
I'll cook.

344
00:25:21,759 --> 00:25:22,599
You'll water the flowers,

345
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:24,519
I'll take care of the kids.

346
00:25:31,599 --> 00:25:32,599
If at that time,

347
00:25:32,599 --> 00:25:34,000
we could have children of our own,

348
00:25:34,359 --> 00:25:35,079
that would be even better.

349
00:25:36,359 --> 00:25:36,720
Right?

350
00:25:49,559 --> 00:25:49,920
Right?

351
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:07,079
Feihu will take you to the airport in a bit.

352
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,000
When I'm done with my business,

353
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,799
I'll meet you at the airport.

354
00:27:12,279 --> 00:27:12,720
Wait for me.

355
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,279
Wait for me.

356
00:27:46,319 --> 00:27:47,000
Ji Zhijie.

357
00:29:06,039 --> 00:29:07,160
He has already set off.
